article_title: Tenet Swings to Loss Amid Charges
article_text:
Tenet Healthcare Corp. reported that it swung to a quarterly loss Monday after sustaining $135 million in after-tax costs that include impairment, restructuring and acquisition-related charges.

Shares of the company slipped 5.5% after hours to $24.10.

Looking ahead, Tenet said it expects annual revenue between $18.8 billion and $19.2...
